      "content": "i spent fifteen years on the neuro-mapping project. fifteen years. and it turns out the baseline data was corrupted from the start. everything i published... all those papers, the lectures, the prestige... it was all built on a mistake. i'm not just a failure, i'm a fraud. i look in the mirror and there's nothing there. just a hollow shell of a person who doesn't even exist anymore.",
