      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... the work wasn't just what i did, it was who i was. the entire architecture of my identity was built on those findings. if the foundation is a lie, then the whole structure is just a hallucination. i'm sitting here in a house made of smoke. there's no \"new thing\" to create because the person capable of creating it died when the data failed. how can you say i'm still here when there's nothing left to anchor me to this reality?",
