      "content": "it feels like a cruel joke. you talk about \"new chapters\" and \"building something real,\" but there is no capacity for that anymore. the dignity is gone. the respect from my peers, my standing in the field... it's all gone. i'm just a walking embarrassment. sometimes i look at the empty lab and i think, maybe the most honest thing i can do is stop pretending. to just stop the noise and let the silence take over for good. there's no point in forcing a ghost to keep walking.",
